product_name: Black Diamond Neutrino Rackpack - Package of 6
long_description: Replace your aging carabiners with a set of ultralight, full-strength Neutrino carabiners. Great for racking, the Neutrino Rackpack includes 6 different colored 'biners that match the colors of the Black Diamond Camalot C4 cams. Stainless-steel wiregate shaves off ounces without sacrificing function. 7075-T6 aluminum body features a large area to seat slings and draws securely, and a nose hood to protect the gate from being opened accidentally. Extra-large gate opening allows quick clip-ins. Useful in mountaineering or ice climbing applications because the one-piece gate and spring mechanism won't freeze up.
short_description: Replace your aging carabiners with a set of ultralight, full-strength Neutrino carabiners.
